{{#content "post-content"}}
<p>I've recently been reading the series of pocket guides published by <a href="http://www.fivesimplesteps.com/" target="_blank">5 Simple Steps</a>. All of these are available digitally for around £2-3 each / £7-8 per set.</p>

<p>I actually found them incredibly useful and really easy to read, so over the next few weeks I'll sum up my thoughts on each collection. In the spirit of the brief concise guides I am talking about, I will keep my reviews bitesize and to the point!</p>

<h2>Five Simple Steps Collection One</h2>
